  "properties": {
    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "#Mood Board Design\r\n\r\n## Do This:\r\n1. Choose one of the fictional brand or event from the options on your canvas.\r\n2. Create a mood board that captures your chosen brand’s vibe. Include:\r\n   - At least 2 colors that match your mood.\r\n   - 1 font style that fits your brand's tone.\r\n   - 1 image that represents your brand's world or feeling.\r\n   - At least 2 style words that describe your brand's personality.\r\n   - (Optional) 1 logo, icon, or background texture that ties your design together.\r\n3. Arrange your items to make the mood clear — how should someone feel when they look at your brand?",
